quran[40]{c,v,t}:
  19,59,"Basi ni yasipwiche panyuma pao isipuka (ŵanache ni isukulu yakusakala), ŵasijonasile swala (pangasilondesya chenene kasiswali kakwe kapena kusileka kwene), ni ŵakuyiye isako (yao), ni tachija kusimangana nao Moto"
  19,60,"Ikaŵeje aŵala ŵatesile toba, ni kulupilila, ni kutendaga yambone, basi ŵanganyao takajinjile ku Mbepo, soni ngaja kutendedwa lupuso pa chilichose"
  19,61,"(Takagajinjile) Matimbe Gandamo, agala gataŵene nao chilanga (Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji achikapolo Ŵakwe mwangali kugaona. Chisimu Jwalakwe chilanga Chakwe chiŵele chakwika"
  19,62,"Ngaaja kupikana mwalakwemo maloŵe gangali mate, ikaŵeje salâm (kulamuchila kwantendele), soni akwete kupata lisiki lyao mwalakwemo kundaŵi ni kwigulo"
  19,63,Jalakwejo ni Mbepo jatukaape kujitawala mwa achikapolo Ŵetu ŵaŵaliji ŵawoga (wakun’jogopa Allah)
  19,64,"Ni ngatukasatulukaga (uwwe Achimalaika) ikaŵeje kwalilamusi lya Ambuje ŵenu (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ), iŵele Yakwe yaili paujo petu ni yapanyuma petu kwisa soni yaili chilikati chayalakweyo, ni nganaŵa Ambuje ŵenu ŵanti ni kuliŵalila"
  19,65,"M’mbuje jwa kumawunde ni petaka ni chilikati cha iŵiliyi, basi mun’galagatileje (Jwele pejo), soni jendelechelani kupilila pakun’galagatila Jwalakwe. Ana pana jwankummanyilila jwakulandana Najo pakolanjidwa"
  19,66,"Sano mundu (kafili) ni akutiji: “Ana ndili mbwile, nambo yakuona chinjikoposyedwa (m’malembe) ni kuŵa ni umi?”"
  19,67,Ana mundu ngaakukumbuchila kuti chisimu Uwwe twan’gumbile jwalakwejo kalakala kutendaga nganaŵa chilichose
  19,68,"Basi ngwalumbila Ambuje ŵenu! Chisimu Uwwe tuchasonganganya ŵanganyao pampepe ni mashetani, kaneka ni tuchiika nao kusyene mungulugulu mwa Jahannama ali chitindiŵalile"
  19,69,Kaneko ni tuchikoposya kusyene kuumila mwikuga lililyose jwalijose mwa ŵanganyao jwaŵaliji jwakupelenganya nnope pakunnyosya (Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji
  19,70,"Soni chisimu Uwwe, ni ŵatukwamanya chenene ŵali ŵakuŵajilwa kuujinjila walakwe (Motowo)"
  19,71,"Soni pangali jwalijose mwa jenumanja ikaŵeje chakaujomboche (Motowo), chiŵele (chalakwechi) kwa Ambuje ŵenu chilamusi chelamulelamule"
  19,72,"Kaneko ni chitukaajokole aŵala ŵaŵaliji ni woga (wakun’jogopa Allah), ni chitukaaleche mwalakwemo ŵalupuso ali chitindiŵalile"
  19,73,"Sano naga gachisoomedwaga kukwao ma Ȃya Getu gakupikanika chenene, aŵala ŵaakanile akasatiji kwa aŵala ŵaakulupilile: “Ana lyapi mwa makuga gaŵili (lyajenumanja kapena lyetuwe) lyalili ni malo gambone nnope gakutama soni lyalili nganya jambone nnope (jakuchimbichika)?”"
  19,74,"Ana jilingwa mwa mikutula jatwajijonasile paujo pao, jajakwete ndundu syambone nnope kwisa soni kaoneche kambone"
  19,75,"Jilani (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ): “Mundu jwali nkusokonechela, basi (Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji channundile jwalakwejo ndaŵi (jaumi wakwe), kwikanila pandema jataachiiona yaakuŵa nkupedwa chilanga – mwine ilagasyo kapena ndaŵi (jakwichila Kiyama) – basi tachimanyilila kuti nduni jwakwete malo gakusakala ni jwaakwete asilikali ŵangali machilili.”"
  19,76,"Sano Allah ni akwajonjechesyaga chongoko ŵandu ŵaajongweche, soni masengo gambone gakwendelechela ni gagali gambone nnope kwa Ambuje ŵenu pa malipilo, soni ni kwakuujila kwambone (ngaŵa ya duniya yaakutwanjila achimakafiliyo)"
  19,77,"Ana mum’bweni ajula jwaagakaaniile ma Ȃya Getu, ni kuŵecheta kuti: “Chisimu chene une (naga kumbuchisya soni ku umi pa Kiyama), chinjipedwa (soni) chipanje ni ŵanache (yaatite pakuumba pa duniya pano).”"
  19,78,"Ana jutekuilingula yakusisika, kapena jutaŵene chilanga ni (Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji"
  19,79,"Ngwamba! Uwwe chitulembe yajukuŵecheta, ni tuchin’jonjechesya ndaŵi jelewu nnope jailagasyo"
  19,80,"Ni tuchintawalila (pajuchiwapo) yosope yajukwambayo (chipanje ni ŵanache ŵakweo), ni juchituichilila (ku Kiyama) juli jikajikape"
  19,81,"Eti ŵanganyao alitendele milungu jinepe kunneka Allah, kuti jape ŵanganyao machili ni uchimbichimbi"
  19,82,"Ngwamba! (Ŵaakuti achimilungu ŵaowo) tachikukana kwagalagatila kwaoko, ni tachisyuka kuŵa atinda ŵao"
  19,83,Ana ngankuiona yanti Uwwe tukugatumisyaga mashetani pa achimakafili gagakwakwembelechesyaga kusyene (kutenda yakusakala)
  19,84,"Basi ngasintenda chitema pa ŵanganyao (kuti apedwe ilagasyo mwachitema), chisimu Uwwe tukuŵa tulinkwaŵalanjila ŵanganyao chiŵalanjilo (chamasiku gao, pachigakwanapo tuchapa ilagasyo)"
  19,85,"Lisiku lyatuchasonganganya ŵandu ŵawoga (wakun’jogopa Allah) ulendo wa kwa (Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji, ali m’mikutula jekwele mu yakwela"
  19,86,Ni tuchasakula akuleŵa wa ku Jahannama ali ni njota (mpela yaikasatiji pakusakulidwa ilango yanjota wakukumwa mesi)
  19,87,Ngasakola machili gakuchondelela ikaŵeje jwapochele chilanga (cha lusa) kuumila kwa (Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji
  19,88,"Ŵanganyao ni akutiji: “(Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji alitendele mwanache.”"
  19,89,Chisimu pamasile pam’biche nacho chindu chakunyalaya kusyene (pa yankuŵechetayi)
  19,90,"Mawunde gakusigalaga panandi kuti gapasuchepasuche ni maloŵego, nombe litaka ganjikaganjika, nombe matumbi kugwa ni katikakatika"
  19,91,Ligongo lyakunnambuchisya (Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji kuti jwana mwanache
  19,92,Soni nganiiŵa yakuŵajilwa kwa (Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji kulitendela mwanache
  19,93,Pangali jwalijose jwaali kumawunde ni petaka ikaŵeje chijuchiyika kwa (Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji juli kapolo
  19,94,"Chisimu pamasile paŵakusenye ŵanganyao pakwamanya chenene, ni ŵaŵalasile chiŵalanjilo chakwana"
  19,95,Soni ŵosope ŵeneo tachim’bichilila (Allah) lisiku lya Kiyama jikajika
  19,96,"Chisimu aŵala ŵaakulupilile ni kutendaga yambone, (Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji tachaŵichila ŵanganyao chinonyelo"
  19,97,"Basi chisimu tujijepepesye jele (Qur’aniji) m’chiŵecheto chenu (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ), kuti mwasengwasye najo ŵandu ŵawoga (wakun’jogopa Allah), ni kwatetela najo ŵandu ŵamakani"
  19,98,Ana jilingwa mwa mikutula jatwajijonasile paujo pao? Ana pana jwalijose jwankum’bona (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) mwa jamanjao kapena kupikana nswakanyo wakwe